com.salesforce.omakase.util

Class As

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.omakase.util.As

  • public final class As
extends Object
    Helper for constructing toString() methods...cuz guava's helper just doesn't get the job done.

    Example: 

    As.string(this).indent().add("abc", abc).toString();

      • fields

        public As fields()
        Specifies that all fields should be added.

        Fields with a value of null will not be output. Iterables will be added with add(String, Iterable) and indent() will automatically be turned on upon the first addition of an iterable. If the object being printed is a Syntax unit, line, column, and comments information will automatically be added.

        Returns:
        this, for chaining.
